Source_name.0: STA>Solar Terrestrial Relations Observatory . of the Sun-Earth Line

Data_type.0: l2-magplasma-1m>Level-2 combined Mag and Plasma 1-minute average

Descriptor.0: impact>In-situ Measurements of Particles and CME Transients_Magnetometer

TEXT.0: The file contains Level 2 magnetic field vectors from the IMPACT/MAG instrument and solar wind parameters from the PLASTIC instrument on the STEREO Ahead spacecraft.

Logical_source_description.0: STEREO Ahead IMPACT/MAG Magnetic Field and PLASTIC Solar Wind Plasma Data

MODS.0: Started from March 1, 2020, the calculation formula for Variable Dynamic_Pressure has been changed from using Variable Vp_RTN (solar wind proton speed) to using Variable Vp (proton bulk speed) in response to that no sensible value of Vp_RTN has been available since the above date.

LINK_TEXT.0: Experiment and Data descriptions for STEREO/IMPACT

VarAttributes.CATDESC: If the total B field is greater than this value, that data point is filtered out and the B field replaced with fill values. It is expected that such values are spurious and non-physical.
